{"tid":781928,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【台灣瘋傳】伴侶行蹤全掌握！《Zenly》追蹤實時位置連手機電量都知","createTime":"2018-08-16T09:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T10:00:16.000Z","uid":55981,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f301ea8a0b199e2c43af43a0b210e10942954617","tid":781928,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:53:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2138611/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E3%80%91%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4%E5%85%A8%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8AZenly%E3%80%8B%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4%E5%AF%A6%E6%99%82%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%80%A3%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%BB%E9%87%8F%E9%83%BD%E7%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2138611%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E4%25BE%25B6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%258F%25A1%25EF%25BC%2581%25E3%2580%258AZenly%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%2583%25BD%25E7%259F%25A5&d=Pl9Y0NndIBa%2F5fkSG1v2xQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=f0d32bdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2138611/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E3%80%91%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%B6%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4%E5%85%A8%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8AZenly%E3%80%8B%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4%E5%AF%A6%E6%99%82%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%80%A3%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%BB%E9%87%8F%E9%83%BD%E7%9F%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2138611/zenly_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2138611%2Fzenly_1024.jpg&h=115fa611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近於台灣社交平台上，瘋傳一個社交手機程式 ──《Zenly》，《Zenly》是一款可以實時追蹤朋友的手機 App，特別之處在於它還可以實時知道朋友的手機電量，連朋友的手機正在充電也知道，甚至是朋友的所在地天氣氣溫及移動時速也可知道，而且 App 內亦有聊天功能和簡單的友情記錄。對於不想被另一半實時追蹤的朋友而言，這個《Zenly》絕對是「危險品」！<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=Pl9Y0NndIBa%2F5fkSG1v2xQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=27b0e343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者今次就試一試這類 App，看其有多「恐怖」！<br />\n<br />\n【熱門報道】Gmail 信件追蹤秘技 郵件已讀與否即時知<br />\n<br />\n使用《Zenly》方便簡單，用戶要先下載《Zenly》 (下載位置：Android、iOS)，然後使用手機號碼進行驗證註冊。程式會要求長期取用用戶手機的定位位置及存取通訊錄，完成後就可以從通訊錄中或輸入電話號碼，把朋友加為 Zenly 好友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2138611/180815_zenly_9_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2138611%2F180815_zenly_9_600.jpg&h=83eb759e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n互相成為好友後，就可以開始追蹤好友的實時位置，點選好友的頭像更可以查看好友當時的手機電量。假若好友正在充電，圖像更會顯示成充電中。於 Zenly 內用戶更可以啟用聊天及群組聊天功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2138611/4a4e07a5-f026-4094-a31b-f7292a31cf9c_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2138611%2F4a4e07a5-f026-4094-a31b-f7292a31cf9c_600.jpg&h=fabf3c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，很多因素也會影響定位的準確度，小記測試時，友人表示一直在停留在固定位置沒有移動，但於 App 中卻顯示友人在該位置附近不斷徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n【熱門報道】18％ 家長追蹤子女網上行為<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，當被追蹤的朋友在乘車移動時，程式更會顯示他的移動時速；當停留時，就會顯示停留時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2138611/180815_zenly_5_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2138611%2F180815_zenly_5_600.jpg&h=86e1381f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Zenly》會顯示朋友所在地的天氣，不過於小記測試時，看見友人的畫面一直出現下雨動畫，但友人卻表示當時該地方天朗氣清，更即時拍攝一張天晴圖片傳送過來，可見天氣預測部分，不太準確。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2138611/180815_zenly_4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2138611%2F180815_zenly_4_600.jpg&h=1d447470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Zenly》更可讓用戶檢視彼此的距離、統計與友人的親密度與見面天數等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2138611/180815_zenly_6_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2138611%2F180815_zenly_6_600.jpg&h=f17feaef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使下載了程式也會有不想被「監控」的時候，程式內也有隱藏位置的功能，點選「幽靈」的圖示後會有 3 個選項，分別是：「精確定點」、「模糊定點」及「凍結定點」，就能把自己的位置調整成只顯示用家附近的位置，或令朋友只看到最後的位置，不再收到位置更新。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2138611/180815_zenly_3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2138611%2F180815_zenly_3_600.jpg&h=69dc9dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，小記提提大家，家人、朋友與兩性之間的關係相當講求信任，凡事也要適可而止，互相尊重，科技若能用在合適的地方，方可改善人類生活。此外，設有追蹤功能的 App 其實選擇很多，即使是香港人常用的《Whatsapp》也能分享實時位置，更能每次設定讓對方查看的時間。"},{"pid":"27200a3b1a9502f2448d3cde9f3190ffd9f3d802","tid":781928,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"d9c80a14f496413701fea57b5672ce2cca871a50","tid":781928,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"想公開比人監察我<br />\n有無人做我伴侶"},{"pid":"724d7c504fe0ae6f5bb6b0660af48db6b6beada3","tid":781928,"uid":31957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c80a14f496413701fea57b5672ce2cca871a50","tid":781928,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"想公開比人監察我<br />\n有無人做我伴侶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"好 我做"},{"pid":"685b88c5a2c65b0c06e47566e1b2408d712e1fb4","tid":781928,"uid":146150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"都要對方都有裝個app 先得"}]}